hello v0.1 README
-----------------

The code in this project is licensed under GPLv3 license.

Hello is a program that says hello, world.
This program is useful to learn the basics about C


BUILD
-----

To build the software it is necessary to install these tools:

==> autoconf , automake , libtool

Create the configuration files with the tool autoheader, autoconf.

$ autoreconf -fi
$ aclocal
$ autoconf
$ automake --add-missing
$ autoreconf -fi
$ rm -rf autom4te.cache config.h.in~


CONFIGURATION
-------------

./configure
 make
 make install


